<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.2">
<l>koṅkuṅ kuṭantaiyum kōṭṭiyū rumpēru</l>
<l>meṅkun tirintu viḷaiyāṭu meṉmakaṉ</l>
<l>caṅkam piṭikkun taṭakkaikkut takkana</l>
<l>laṅka muṭaiyatōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">varakku vaḻittatōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff with good form,</l>
<l>suitable for the broad hand, that holds the conch,</l>
<l>of my son who plays, wandering everywhere</l>
<l>– Koṅku, Kuṭantai, Kōṭṭiūr, and Pēr.</l>
<l>Bring a staff smeared with vermilion.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
